item.title: Switching from Eudora/Mac to Pine
item.description: inessential.com: Switching from Eudora/Mac to Pine "I recently switched from Eudora/Mac, which I used for many years, to Pine [on OS X]. Why the hell would I do a thing like that? I had a few reasons."

item.title: Symmetric Cryptography in Perl
item.description: Perl.com: Symmetric Cryptography in Perl "Having purchased the $250 cookie recipe from Neiman-Marcus, Alice wants to send it to Bob, but keep it away from Eve, who snoops on everyone's network traffic from the cubicle down the hall. How can Perl help her?"
